**Headers/Titles:**
- Enriched with coconut for intensive moisture

**Labels/Tags:**

**Ingredients:**
- AQUA, GLYCERIN, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, GLYCERETH-26, PENTYLENEGLYCOL, CARBOMER, SACCHARIDE ISOMERATE, GLYCERYL ACRYLATE/ACRYLIC ACID COPOLYMER, PEG-40 HYDROGENATED CASTOR OIL, BUTYLENE GLYCOL, 1,2-HEXANEDIOL, PHENOXYETHANOL, TRIETHANOLAMINE, SODIUM HYALURONATE, POLYGLYCERYL-10 laurate, HYDROLYZED COLLAGEN, GLYCYRRHIZA URALENSIS ROOT EXTRACT, PORTULACA OLERACEA EXTRACT, PAEONIA SUFFRUTICOSA ROOT BARK EXTRACT, METHYLPARABEN, OLIGOPEPTIDE-1, CITRUS PARADISI FRUIT EXTRACT, PAPAIN, CHONDRUS CRISPUS (CARRAGEENAN) EXTRACT, PHASEOLUS RADIATUS SEED EXTRACT, PANTHENOL, HYDROGENATED LECITHIN, 1,2-HEXANEDIOL, SODIUM POLYACRYLOYLDIMETHYL TAURATE, GLYCERYL ACRYLATE/ACRYLIC ACID COPOLYMER, ROSA RUGOSA LEAF EXTRACT, OCIMUM BASILICUM (BASIL) EXTRACT, PHENOXYETHANOL, CITRUS LIMON (LEMON) FRUIT EXTRACT, SCUTELLARIA BAICALENSIS ROOT EXTRACT, CAMELLIA SINENSIS LEAF EXTRACT, ROSMARINUS OFFICINALIS LEAF EXTRACT.

**Effect:**
- Contains coconut extract, skin conditioning, lock the skin drink nutrients, repair the damage caused by dehydration, make the skin hydrated and tender, improve the dull and tired skin, soothe and repair the skin, add hyaluronic acid, effectively penetrate the skin, moisturize, effectively moisturizing, make the skin more elastic, full of elasticity.

**Usage:**
- After cleansing the face, take off the package, take out the mask and unfold it, stick it on the face and gently press the mask with your fingers to make it close to the face completely, relax and enjoy 15-20 minutes, let the skin fully absorb the essence, and cost water wash off the remaining essence.

**Cautions:**
1. Store in a dry and cool place, avoid direct sun exposure.
2. If any discomfort or allergic symptoms occur, please discontinue using immediately and consult a physician if necessary.
3. Not to be used for children under three years of age.
